      "content": "i tried some acetaminophen earlier and it didnt really do much. i'm just trying to get through the work day. i know i'm supposed to be careful but isn't a standard dose of ibuprofen usually fine? like i don't plan on taking more than one pill, it shouldn't be a big deal if it's just a one-time thing for the pain, right?",
